Connection with Eulerian numbers
There are formulas connecting Eulerian numbers ⟨nm⟩ to Bernoulli numbers:

  
    
      
        
          
            
              
                
                  ∑
                  
                    m
                    =
                    0
                  
                  
                    n
                  
                
                (
                −
                1
                
                  )
                  
                    m
                  
                
                
                  ⟨
                  
                    
                      n
                      m
                    
                  
                  ⟩
                
              
              
                
                =
                
                  2
                  
                    n
                    +
                    1
                  
                
                (
                
                  2
                  
                    n
                    +
                    1
                  
                
                −
                1
                )
                
                  
                    
                      B
                      
                        n
                        +
                        1
                      
                    
                    
                      n
                      +
                      1
                    
                  
                
                ,
              
            
            
              
                
                  ∑
                  
                    m
                    =
                    0
                  
                  
                    n
                  
                
                (
                −
                1
                
                  )
                  
                    m
                  
                
                
                  ⟨
                  
                    
                      n
                      m
                    
                  
                  ⟩
                
                
                  
                    
                      
