    {\displaystyle (1-p^{m-1}){\frac {B_{m}}{m}}\equiv (1-p^{n-1}){\frac {B_{n}}{n}}{\pmod {p^{b}}}.}
  Since Bn = −nζ(1 − n), this can also be written

  
    
      
        
